          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/5df6e0261705deb19cfc26f239251c85_5998111632103396481.png",
                "id": "talent70025",
                "key": "旋尾迅击",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "旋尾迅击"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，抓1张<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">噬骸能量块</span>；然后，手牌中每有1张<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">噬骸能量块</span>，抓1张牌（每回合最多抓2张）。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/c810824214ed1ed7d4c4519a109c0ba5_8751126126869155859.png",
                "id": "talent98666",
                "key": "盘绕风引",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "盘绕风引"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">舍弃</span>手牌中所有的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">噬骸能量块</span>，每<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">舍弃</span>2张，此次伤害翻倍1次。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/1d8d506cdab76fd7660ea285c094d231_9084505341280970854.png",
                "id": "talent64046",
                "key": "错落风涡",
                "materials": [],
